            <h2>Basic grid</h2>
            <p>The Grid. A digital frontier. I tried to picture clusters of information as they moved through the computer. What did they look like? Ships? motorcycles? Were the circuits like freeways? I kept dreaming of a world I thought I'd never see. And then, one day...</p>
            <p>Sorry got carried away, Start by simply adding an element with the class <code>row</code>. This will give you your block that will contain your columns set to a width of 1200px. Next add your columns with the classes of <code>grid-1</code> all the way to <code>grid-12</code> depending on your design.</p>
